$ /var/lib/apt/lists

`/var/lib/apt/lists` is the *storage area for state information for each package resource specified in `sources.list`* (for example `→ Linux/fhs/etc/apt/sources_list`)


sa:

  The `→ Linux/fhs/var/lib/apt/lists/lock` file.

  The `--list-cleanup` option of `→ Linux/package-managers/APT/commands/apt-get`
